      "content": "oh man i dont think i was prescribed any antibiotics for this one specifically, the doctor just said it would heal on its own. would it be okay if i just put some antibiotic cream on it from the chemist and use a warm compress a few times a day to help it clear up? feel like i can manage it at home if i just keep it clean",
